\par \bullet  Removal of associates or items whose alignment or personality is distasteful to the item. 
\par \bullet  The character divesting him or herself of all other magic items or items of a certain type. 
\par \bullet  Obedience from the character so the item can direct where they go for its own purposes. 
\par \bullet  Immediate seeking out and slaying of creatures hateful to the item. 
\par \bullet  Magical protections and devices to protect the item from molestation when it is not in use. 
\par \bullet  That the character carry the item with him or her on all occasions. 
\par \bullet  That the character relinquish the item in favor of a more suitable possessor due to alignment differences or conduct. 
\par 
