\par \bullet  Force its possessor into combat. 
\par \bullet  Refuse to strike opponents. 
\par \bullet  Strike at its wielder or his or her associates. 
\par \bullet  Force its possessor to surrender to an opponent. 
\par \bullet  Cause itself to drop from the character\rquote s grasp. 
